data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS, BEST AND FINAL OFFER DEADLINE OF 8PM 02/17/24. You must see this charming brick ranch nestled on .60 acres, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience! Boasting 3 bedrooms, 1.5bathrooms, and hardwood floors, this home provides comfortable living spaces for all. Enjoy the convenience of a carport and the luxury ofwalking distance access to the beloved Doodle Trail, ideal for outdoor enthusiasts. Additionally, a short drive brings you to downtown Easley,where a myriad of dining and shopping options await. Don't miss the chance to call this delightful property your own and enjoy the best of bothworlds – peaceful suburban living and easy access to urban amenities!
